snippet: The S.U.V. driver accused of causing a car to crash into a Winter Park day care on Wednesday, killing a 4-year-old girl and injuring 14 other people, most of them children, surrendered to the authorities on Thursday.
abstract: Robert Alex Corchado, SUV driver accused of causing car to crash into a Winter Park, Fla, day care, surrenders to authorities; crash killed 4-year-old girl and injured 14 other people, most of them children.
lead_paragraph: The S.U.V. driver accused of causing a car to crash into a Winter Park day care on Wednesday, killing a 4-year-old girl and injuring 14 other people, most of them children, surrendered to the authorities on Thursday.

headline.main: Florida: Driver Sought in Crash at Day Care Center Is in Custody
headline.print_headline: Florida: Driver Sought in Crash at Day Care Center Is in Custody
